collections.name: Microcosm
collections.description:
"Microcosm" is YASHIMA STUDIOS' first project, released as a limited edition of 100 unique pieces.
The work explores the infinite possibilities hidden within the everyday.
It serves as a reminder that people rarely contemplate the true nature of the visual information they encounter daily—whether it's the coffee they drink in the morning or the screen they stare at while purchasing an NFT.
The true essence of things exists in a state of possibility, manifesting into reality only through observation.

collections.name: Hay Fever
collections.description: "Hay Fever" is an Orangehare In-House production that revels in the beauty of obsession—bright, overwhelming, impossible to ignore. Sunflowers stretch toward the sun, faces bloom with warmth or wilt in shadow, and somewhere between nostalgia and overexposure, a red fever takes hold. Is it love? Longing? Or just the dizzying effect of standing too close for too long? Inspired by the golden hues of Van Gogh and the haze of early spring, this collection of 38 unique one-of-one NFTs lingers like pollen in the air—inescapable, intoxicating, and just a little too much. Designed and brought to life through Orangehare’s in-house production process, including real paint and previous orangehare artists.
